title: HPE 3PAR: Capacity
agents: 3par
catalog: hw/storagehw/hpe
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check measures the total space of the filer and total space
 for each type of disk. It's behaviour is like a regular filesystem.
 You can define thresholds as known by other filesystem checks.

 If there is failed space the check will go {CRIT} and show how
 many MiBs has been failed.

inventory:
 One service is created for each device type and one summary service.
